{{see|eve}}

==English==

===Etymology===
Greek [[Εύα]] (Eva) < Hebrew [[חוה|חַוָּה]] (havah) = 'life, lively, giving life'.

===Proper noun===
'''Eve'''

# according to the [[Bible]] and [[Qur'an]], the first [[woman]] and [[mother]] of the [[human race]]; [[Adam]]'s [[wife]]

